195
00:17:16,077 --> 00:17:17,078
Well, I still did it.

196
00:17:17,161 --> 00:17:19,121
Oh, so that makes you
father of the year now?

197
00:17:19,204 --> 00:17:20,498
At least you've got a father.

198
00:17:20,580 --> 00:17:22,500
