for shit you screwed up.

199
00:17:22,583 --> 00:17:25,461
He left like 40 years ago.
Get over it.

200
00:17:25,545 --> 00:17:27,463
God knows I'm not gonna be defined by you.

201
00:17:27,547 --> 00:17:30,132
Are you kidding me?
After all we have done for you?

202
00:17:30,216 --> 00:17:32,718
