253
00:21:48,766 --> 00:21:50,101
And pretty weird.

254
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:52,144
Well done.

255
00:21:52,228 --> 00:21:55,398
Yeah, honestly, I wish I could have
forgotten a whole year when I was a kid.

256
00:21:56,983 --> 00:21:58,818
